section.div: Implementation of the Surya Foundation Model and Downstream Tasks for Heliophysics
Semantic search and document parsing tools for the command line

div.div:
feat(tui): add modals for export, health report, and settings configuration
- Implemented ExportModal for configuring proxy export with various formats and filters. - Created HealthReportModal to display proxy health information with interactive tabs. - Developed SettingsModal for application configuration, allowing users to adjust cache and rotation settings. - Introduced enhanced styling for modals and widgets to improve user experience. - Added ProxyStatsWidget and EnhancedProgressWidget for real-time proxy statistics and progress tracking. - Implemented ProxyDataTable and ProxyTableWidget for displaying proxy data with rich formatting and functionality.
